# Laravel Multi-Platform Chat Application Structure

This is a Laravel application that handles multi-platform chat functionality for Telegram, VK, and external traffic sources.

## Key Entry Points
- [artisan](mdc:artisan) - Laravel command-line interface
- [public/index.php](mdc:public/index.php) - Main web entry point
- [bootstrap/app.php](mdc:bootstrap/app.php) - Application bootstrap

## Core Application Structure

### Controllers
- [app/Http/Controllers/TelegramBotController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/TelegramBotController.php) - Handles Telegram webhook requests
- [app/Http/Controllers/VkBotController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/VkBotController.php) - Handles VK webhook requests
- [app/Http/Controllers/ExternalTrafficController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/ExternalTrafficController.php) - Manages external traffic sources

### Services
- [app/Services/Telegram/](mdc:app/Services/Telegram/) - Telegram-specific services
- [app/Services/VK/](mdc:app/Services/VK/) - VK-specific services
- [app/Services/External/](mdc:app/Services/External/) - External platform services
- [app/Services/Redis/RedisService.php](mdc:app/Services/Redis/RedisService.php) - Redis operations

### Models
- [app/Models/Message.php](mdc:app/Models/Message.php) - Core message model
- [app/Models/BotUser.php](mdc:app/Models/BotUser.php) - Bot user management
- [app/Models/ExternalMessage.php](mdc:app/Models/ExternalMessage.php) - External platform messages

### DTOs
- [app/DTOs/](mdc:app/DTOs/) - Data Transfer Objects for API responses
- [app/DTOs/Telegram/](mdc:app/DTOs/Telegram/) - Telegram-specific DTOs
- [app/DTOs/Vk/](mdc:app/DTOs/Vk/) - VK-specific DTOs

